Saiph
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- this class should probably have way more methods. examples:
  + find key for slot with item (see private methods in Unihorn)
  + figure out if wielded weapon/worn armor [on slot] is cursed, and thus
    preventing us from eg. using a pick-axe, putting on rings, etc.
  + probably lots more...


