Wand
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- does not handle wands that generate no message.
- currently it appears to rely on Elbereth to write a message. it shouldn't do
  this, the idea is that every analyzer should work independently.
  also, Elbereth is only capable of engraving in dust with finger, engraving
  with wand of digging makes the game crash.


